data.description: Discover the charm of this 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom haven in North Point Subdivision. A tastefully remodeled interior awaits, with attention to detail evident in the beautifully updated bathrooms. The kitchen is a focal point, showcasing rich dark wood cabinets that add warmth and sophistication. Step into the backyard oasis with carefully laid pavers, creating an ideal space for outdoor gatherings.    Noteworthy additions include a new garage door, enhancing both aesthetics and functionality. Embrace the allure of nature with fruit trees gracing the property. Completing the package is a convenient one-car garage, making this home a delightful blend of style and practicality.  Close proximity to I-275 which facilitates access to Down Town Tampa, Busch Gardens Etc
